-q` - Suppress non-error output\n- `--version` - Show version and exit\n- `--help`, `-h` - Show help\n\n### API Key Management\n\nThe tool resolves API keys in this order:\n1. **Environment variable:** `IMAGE_CREATOR_API_KEY`\n2. **System keyring:** Stored via the `keyring` library at `image-creator` service / `openrouter_api_key` account\n\n### Create Command Details\n\n**Arguments:**\n- `prompt` - Text prompt for image generation (required)\n\n**Options:**\n- `--model` - OpenRouter model ID (default: `google/gemini-3-pro-image-preview`)\n- `--out`, `-o` - Output path (default: `~/generated-images/`)\n- `--aspect-ratio` - Supported: 1:1, 2:3, 3:2, 3:4, 4:3, 4:5, 5:4, 9:16, 16:9, 21:9\n- `--image-size` - Supported: 1K, 2K, or 4K\n\n### API Call Details\n\n**Endpoint:** `https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions`\n\n**Request payload structure:**\n```json\n{\n  \"model\": \"<model_id>\",\n  \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"<prompt>\"}],\n  \"modalities\": [\"image\", \"text\"],\n  \"stream\": false,\n  \"image_config\": {\n    \"aspect_ratio\": \"<ratio>\",\n    \"image_size\": \"<size>\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Authentication:** Bearer token in `Authorization` header\n\n**Timeout:** 120 seconds\n\n### Output and Error Handling\n\n**Success output (JSON format):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"image_path\": \"<path>\",\n    \"model\": \"<model_id>\",\n    \"mime_type\": \"<mime>\",\n    \"prompt\": \"<prompt>\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Error output (JSON format):**\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": true,\n  \"code\": \"<ERROR_CODE>\",\n  \"message\": \"<error message>\"\n}\n```\n\n**Exit codes:**\n- `0` - SUCCESS\n- `1` - GENERAL_ERROR\n- `2` - INVALID_ARGS\n- `3` - NOT_FOUND\n- `4` - EXTERNAL_FAILURE (API/network failures)\n\n### Key Implementation Features\n\n1. **Image extraction:** Handles multiple response formats for image URLs:\n   - Direct image URLs\n   - Data URLs (base64-encoded images)\n   - Nested structures (`image_url` or `imageUrl`)\n\n2. **Image saving:**\n   - Extracts MIME type from data URLs\n   - Converts JPEG mime to `.jpg` extension\n   - Creates directory structure as needed\n   - Uses timestamp-based filenames (`image-YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS.<ext>`)\n\n3. **Input validation:**\n   - Validates aspect ratios against supported set\n   - Validates image sizes against supported set\n   - Validates format option (must be \"json\" or \"text\")\n\n4. **Robust error handling:**\n   - Network/request failures\n   - JSON parsing errors\n   - Missing/invalid API responses\n   - Keyring access errors\n\n### File Structure\n```\nimage-creator/\n├── pyproject.toml\n├── src/image_creator/\n│   ├── __init__.py (version: 0.1.0)\n│   └── main.py (452 lines - core implementation)\n└── tests/\n    └── .gitkeep (empty)\n```"}],"totalDurationMs":17261,"totalTokens":20150,"totalToolUseCount":8,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6104,"cache_read_input_tokens":14042,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6104,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q399c3hzsYiKUTJgPzbAEP"}
