t, quiet=quiet)\n```\n\n### Key Patterns\n\n1. **Context Object Storage**: Global options are stored in `ctx.obj` as an `OutputSettings` dataclass in the main callback\n2. **Settings Retrieval**: Each command calls `get_settings(ctx)` to retrieve the settings\n3. **Quiet Mode**: Suppresses all output when enabled (stdout only, not stderr errors)\n4. **Format Options**: \n   - `json`: Default. Returns `{\"success\": true, \"data\": {...}}` or `{\"error\": true, \"code\": \"...\", \"message\": \"...\"}`\n   - `text`: Human-readable format for stdout; errors go to stderr with `CODE: message` format\n5. **Exit Pattern**: All functions use `raise typer.Exit(code)` rather than returning\n6. **Error Output**: Always goes to `stderr`; success output goes to `stdout`\n\nThis is a clean, reusable pattern suitable for adoption in other CLI tools in this project."}],"totalDurationMs":9779,"totalTokens":18514,"totalToolUseCount":3,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":181,"cache_read_input_tokens":17301,"output_tokens":1027,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":181,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TEzdBdDzqBokqyHDbuV2H8"}
